Title: outbound validation in REST API when attributes got deleted
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: rest-api
Date: 1656345725
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.2.0b1

There can be a case where attributes are stored on a host or folder
but the definition of these attributes were deleted. This would then
result in an error on outbound validation.
